OL,3,CPlans approved for Scotland's first
OL,4,CCenter Parcs site
OL,6,FCenter Parcs' plans for its first
OL,7,Fholiday village in Scotland have been
OL,8,Fapproved by Scottish Borders Council.
OL,10,FThe 988-acre (400 ha) site near
OL,11,FHawick, which will be called 'Center
OL,12,FParcs Scottish Borders', will see 700
OL,13,Fholiday lodges, alongside shops and
OL,14,Frestaurants, an indoor swimming
OL,15,Fcomplex and health spa, outdoor
OL,16,Factivities, and man-made lochs, nature
OL,17,Ftrails and woodland.
