OL,6,FThe development, which is expected to
OL,7,Fcost around #450million, received 38
OL,8,Fletters of objection, and six letters
OL,9,Fin support of the plans.
OL,11,FThose local to the site, which is
OL,12,Fabout 4km north of Hawick and 9km
OL,13,Fsouth of Selkirk, raised concerns over
OL,14,Fthe impact to the landscape, loss of
OL,15,Ffarmland, and the potential noise and
OL,16,Flight pollution.
