OL,6,FEconomic and tourist bodies have
OL,7,Flargely expressed their support for
OL,8,Fthe plans, however, with The South of
OL,9,FScotland Destination Alliance
OL,10,Fsuggesting the park could bring
OL,11,Ffurther investment to the area, while
OL,12,FThe British Horse Society approved of
OL,13,Fthe plans' consideration of horse
OL,14,Friding.
OL,16,FCenter Parc bosses claim the holiday
OL,17,Fpark will create more than 1,200 jobs,
OL,18,Fand that it will add #75m a year to
OL,19,Fthe Borders economy.
