OL,6,FOne neighbouring farmer, however, told
OL,7,FITV Border he fears how the holiday
OL,8,Fpark would enclose his land.
OL,10,FMerlin Lewis said: "We are going to be
OL,11,Ffenced in by a structure that more
OL,12,Fclosely resembles a prison enclosure
OL,13,Fthan anything that would divide rural
OL,14,Fland parcels.
