OL,6,F"The nature of the barrier itself,
OL,7,Fwhich Center Parcs are referring to,
OL,8,Fis bunding, which is a very
OL,9,Fsubstantial earth mound, and then a
OL,10,Fmetal impenetrable fence. More along
OL,11,Fthe lines of what you'd expect around,
OL,12,Fan electrical station or something
OL,13,Fwhere security was needed."
OL,15,FIn response to this complaint, Center
OL,16,FParcs told ITV Border: "Before
OL,17,Fsubmitting our planning application,
OL,18,Fwe engaged with more than 1,000
OL,19,Fmembers of the public over eight
OL,20,Fmonths, with that feedback shaping and
OL,21,Frefining our proposals.
