OL,6,FAt Monday's planning meeting,
OL,7,Fmeanwhile, Center Parcs CEO Colin
OL,8,FMcKinlay said: "Center Parcs has an
OL,9,Fextraordinary positive impact on the
OL,10,Fcommunities surrounding its villages.
OL,12,F"When we identified the Borders for
OL,13,Four seventh village we were of course
OL,14,Fattracted by the stunning views, the
OL,15,Frich heritage and of course the warm
OL,16,Fhospitality. But we also saw an
OL,17,Fopportunity to contribute to the goal
OL,18,Fof making the Borders a 'go to not a
OL,19,Fgo through' destination."
