OL,4,CCenter Parcs site
OL,6,FFollowing a site visit last week,
OL,7,Fplanning committee members unanimously
OL,8,Fsupported the application.
OL,10,FCouncillor Donald Moffat said: "I
OL,11,Ffirst got elected onto this committee
OL,12,Fin 1989 and I must say this is one of
OL,13,Fthe most impressive and exciting
OL,14,Fdevelopments I've seen for Hawick and
OL,15,Fthe Borders as a whole."
OL,17,FConstruction work on the site is
OL,18,Fexpected to begin in early 2027, with
OL,19,Fa planned opening date of Spring 2029.
